  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "TOZ KS-23M 23x75 毫米泵动式霰弹枪",
      "en": "TOZ KS-23M 23x75mm pump-action shotgun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "KS-23M",
      "en": "KS-23M"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 18,402₽ | 物品价值: 18,402 | Jaeger报价: 11,041₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 31,591₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级3 < 测量卷尺 x5 + T-Plug x5 + USB-A x5 | Σ ≈ 281,980₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级4 < 软管 x1 + 军用波纹软管 x1 | Σ ≈ 112,413₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 55,290₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 52,650₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < USEC x4 | Σ ≈ 3,600₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Light of the Lotus - Part 5 @ 莲花\n\nKS-23 是一款苏联时期设计制造的霰弹枪。由于其使用了带有膛线的枪管，因此苏联军方将其分类为卡宾枪，KS 即为俄语“特种卡宾枪”的缩写。KS-23 以大口径著称，其发射的子弹尺寸达 23 毫米，约等于英美标准的 6.27 铅径或现行欧洲标准的 4 铅径，是如今口径最大的现役霰弹枪。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 18,402₽ | 物品价值: 18,402 | Jaeger报价: 11,041₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 31,591₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级3 < 测量卷尺 x5 + T-Plug x5 + USB-A x5 | Σ ≈ 281,980₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级4 < 软管 x1 + 军用波纹软管 x1 | Σ ≈ 112,413₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 55,290₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 52,650₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < USEC x4 | Σ ≈ 3,600₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Light of the Lotus - Part 5 @ 莲花\n\nKS-23 is a Russian shotgun, although because it uses a rifled barrel it is officially designated by the Russian military as a carbine. KS stands for Karabin Spetsialniy, \"Special Carbine\". It is renowned for its large caliber, firing a 23 mm round, equating to 6.27 gauge using the British and American standards of shotgun gauges and approximately 4 gauge using the current European standards (based on the metric CIP tables), making it the largest-bore shotgun in use today."
    },
